x4freetext: A Zr-90, Sn-116 and Pb-208 targets with enrichments
more than 97% and with nominal thicknesses of 5.1, 5.0
with a composite focal-plane detector system, which was
developed in the framework of the EuroSuperNova ESN)
.The decay neutrons were observed in coincidence
with the inelastically scattered alpha particles with
the large-coverage detector array(EDEN) placed in the
backward hemisphere with respect to the beam direction.
In present setup the neutron-detector array consisted
of 30 organic-liquid scintillators of type NE213.
A letter about table data was send M.Hunyadi
No reply from the authors. Data were digitized.
